{
  "stem": "21319.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a little baby, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- they were going-- they were driving in with the tanks, with the big tanks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came, you know, and heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Poles were so happy to see them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sorry I have to say that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the Poles were so happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were waving to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Could you believe that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the-- the Russians, they were afraid for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were such anti-Semites, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when the-- when the Germans came in, they became their friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't realize that the Germans will kill them too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't want to face the facts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You mentioned you were with your baby when the-- the bombs were falling?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was running in the cellars, you know, hiding from the bombing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's funny, like, three, four buildings were bombed out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the building where I lived wasn't bombed out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could you believe that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had to run all the way-- I was on the fourth floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to go-- fourth or the fifth, I think-- all the way in the cellars, hiding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did things begin to change for the Jews?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, right away it was-- you couldn't go out certain hours of the day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It became hell, OK?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They start to grab the Jews, and take them to kill them, to-- in mass graves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to shot them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother was killed on the street, walking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Shot.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so was my brother-in-law, one of my sisters' husbands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] husband was killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was-- this-- she was told that he was taken to the [INAUDIBLE], where the-- the police station.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she was running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was running with her to the police station.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
